<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Medical Career Path</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="stream-detail.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="stream-hero">
    <span>Health Science Stream</span>
    <h1>Medical Career Path</h1>
    <p>Medical careers focus on diagnosis, treatment, care, medicines, rehabilitation, and public health. This stream suits students who are patient, observant, science-focused, and motivated to help people.</p>
  </header>

  <main class="stream-shell">
    <section class="quick-grid">
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Main Subjects</strong>Biology, Chemistry, Physics, English</div>
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Common Exams</strong>NEET, CUET, university entrance tests</div>
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Best For</strong>Care, patience, observation, science interest</div>
    </section>

    <h2 class="section-title">Popular Medical Fields</h2>
    <section class="path-grid">
      <div class="path-card active"><h3>Doctor</h3><p>Diagnose illnesses, treat patients, and specialize through MD/MS after MBBS.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Dentistry</h3><p>Focus on oral health, dental surgery, and clinic-based patient care.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Pharmacy</h3><p>Study medicines, drug safety, pharma industry, and pharmacy practice.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Nursing</h3><p>Deliver professional patient care in hospitals, clinics, and community health.</p></div>
    </section>

    <section class="tabs">
      <button class="tab-btn active" data-target="courses">Courses</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="exams">Entrance Exams</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="careers">Careers</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="skills">Skills</button>
    </section>

    <section class="detail-panel">
      <div id="courses" class="tab-panel active">
        <h2>Courses You Can Choose</h2>
        <ul><li>MBBS for becoming a doctor.</li><li>BDS for dentistry.</li><li>B.Pharm or D.Pharm for pharmacy.</li><li>BSc Nursing, Physiotherapy, Lab Technology, Radiology, Nutrition.</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div id="exams" class="tab-panel">
        <h2>Entrance Exams</h2>
        <ul><li>NEET UG for MBBS, BDS, BAMS, BHMS, and many medical programs.</li><li>CUET or university tests for allied health and life science courses.</li><li>Institute-level exams for nursing and paramedical programs.</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div id="careers" class="tab-panel">
        <h2>Career Options</h2>
        <ul><li>Doctor, Dentist, Pharmacist, Nurse, Physiotherapist.</li><li>Lab Technician, Radiologist Assistant, Nutritionist, Public Health Worker.</li><li>Medical Research, Hospital Administration, Pharma Quality Control.</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div id="skills" class="tab-panel">
        <h2>Skills To Build</h2>
        <ul><li>Strong Biology and Chemistry concepts.</li><li>Empathy, patience, communication, and attention to detail.</li><li>Discipline for long study hours and practical training.</li></ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="planner">
      <h2>Student Checklist</h2>
      <label><input type="checkbox"> Review Biology and Chemistry basics weekly.</label>
      <label><input type="checkbox"> Check NEET eligibility and syllabus.</label>
      <label><input type="checkbox"> Compare MBBS, BDS, Nursing, Pharmacy, and Physiotherapy paths.</label>
    </section>

    <div class="back-row"><a class="action-link" href="career.jsp">Back to Career Streams</a></div>
  </main>
  <script src="stream-detail.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
